 are now subscribed Your newsletter sign-up was successful The USA's Kristen Faulkner was not on anyone's radar for theOlympic Gamesone month before she claimed the country's first gold medal in the road race in 40 years.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"score\": 0.9999993389976591, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kristen Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your newsletter sign-up\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone's radar\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's first gold medal\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"40 years\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact at the start of July she wasn't even expected to start the road race - her focus was only on the Team Pursuit event which starts on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.828675473823764e-35, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 559}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"her focus\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However,the 31-year-old from Alaskamade it into the road event in a roundabout way, then beat two of the best female cyclists of all time - Marianne Vos (Netherlands) and Lotte Kopecky (Belgium) - with a searing attack at almost exactly a 4km Team Pursuit distance from the line.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marianne Vos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\"}, {\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999796718841, \"rank\": 2.031030374290704e-08, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lotte Kopecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\"}, {\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.999999996558472, \"rank\": 3.398196441280341e-09, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.828675473823764e-35, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the road event\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"a roundabout way\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"the best female cyclists\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"a searing attack\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Faulkner could hardly believe she won whenshe crossed the line opposite the Eiffel Tower, so much so she did not react with any sort of victory salute until after she had passed the press photographer's pen.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3254571354490144e-18, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whenshe\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"any sort\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"victory salute\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"the press photographer's pen\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew I'd won but to be honest, emotionally, it was a bit surreal for me.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think, even though I came here with the confidence that I could earn a medal when I crossed the line, I did not fully take it in - it was just pretty overwhelming for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the confidence\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Faulkner's journey to the top step of the Olympic road race podium was short and long at the same time.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3254571354490144e-18, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top step\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1478}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic road race podium\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A former rower, she was working in finance after graduating from Harvard.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University\", \"score\": 0.9960275444858503, \"rank\": 0.003640451759695082, \"text\": \"Harvard\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"finance\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had only started riding a bike in 2017 and just over three years ago she left a solid job in New York City to commit to a pro cycling career in 2021.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1719, \"end\": 1732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.500086607190441e-12, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bike\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"a solid job\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"a pro cycling career\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her rise through the ranks has been nothing short of meteoric, but the Olympics on the road were not the pinnacle she was aiming for.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her rise\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"the ranks\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"the pinnacle\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Faulkner missed automatically qualifying for the United States road team by coming second to triathlete Taylor Knibb by just 11 seconds at the individual time trial national championships in May.\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1911, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3254571354490144e-18, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}, {\"begin\": 1960, \"end\": 1973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999996484799047, \"rank\": 3.2905687562070935e-07, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taylor Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just 11 seconds\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual time\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"trial national championships\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result she returned her focus to the Team Pursuit, which she had been training toward for over a year.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2149, \"end\": 2161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.828675473823764e-35, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"her focus\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"over a year\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her road race ambitions suddenly became a reality when, on July 9, USA Cycling announced that Knibb declined her position on the team for the road event since she lacked bunch racing experience, and suddenly Faulkner was in the road race alongside Chlo\\u00e9 Dygert.\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2283, \"end\": 2294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9830633032563941e-41, \"text\": \"USA Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\"}, {\"begin\": 2310, \"end\": 2315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.9998482442329574, \"rank\": 0.00015177880044182828, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}, {\"begin\": 2424, \"end\": 2432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3254571354490144e-18, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}, {