.0, \"rank\": 3.828675473823764e-35, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two days\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reason is that I think we have a really strong team for the Team Pursuit.\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2830, \"end\": 2842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.828675473823764e-35, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reason\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"a really strong team\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we are medal capable.\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so I really had to ask myself, 'am I medal capable in the road race as well?'\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because ultimately, USA Cycling wants us to wear medals, and that's why we are here,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2976, \"end\": 2987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9830633032563941e-41, \"text\": \"USA Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are medal capable in the Team Pursuit, and it was a big risk for me to do the road race, because I may or may not be more fatigued having done the road race before the Team Pursuit.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3082, \"end\": 3094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.828675473823764e-35, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}, {\"begin\": 3225, \"end\": 3237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.828675473823764e-35, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big risk\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3117}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3144}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I had to really sit down with my coaches.\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my coaches\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to assess, could I really win a medal in the road race?\\\"\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was just the kind of careful analysis and risk assessment that she trained for in her previous life in venture capital, and the risk most definitely paid off.\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the kind\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3368}, {\"ngram\": \"careful analysis\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3388}, {\"ngram\": \"risk assessment\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3408}, {\"ngram\": \"her previous life\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"venture capital\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3469}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision for Faulkner to compete in the road race was not the result of a sudden change of heart by Knibb, she revealed in the post-race press conference.\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3528, \"end\": 3536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3254571354490144e-18, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}, {\"begin\": 3615, \"end\": 3620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.9998482442329574, \"rank\": 0.00015177880044182828, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3523}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3564}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3583}, {\"ngram\": \"a sudden change\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3602}, {\"ngram\": \"heart\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"the post-race press conference\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The last few months and the last week in particular, were a lot of discussions with me and USA Cycling and with my coaches to figure out how I could perform today and how to maximise my recovery for team pursuit if I do it.\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3763, \"end\": 3774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9830633032563941e-41, \"text\": \"USA Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The last few months\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3691}, {\"ngram\": \"the last week\", \"from\": 3696, \"to\": 3709}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3735}, {\"ngram\": \"discussions\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3750}, {\"ngram\": \"my coaches\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3794}, {\"ngram\": \"my recovery\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3866}, {\"ngram\": \"team pursuit\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually did a lot of race simulations as part of my training, followed by an easy day, followed by a track day.\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 4012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3918}, {\"ngram\": \"race simulations\", \"from\": 3922, \"to\": 3938}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3946}, {\"ngram\": \"my training\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 3961}, {\"ngram\": \"an easy day\", \"from\": 3975, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"a track day\", \"from\": 4000, \"to\": 4011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through those race simulations, I found that I recovered quite well and that I could show up to the track and be quite ready for the race.\", \"from\": 4013, \"to\": 4151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those race simulations\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4043}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 4109, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 4142, \"to\": 4150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I made an agreement with my track coaches that I would only do the road race if I felt that I was medal capable, and if at any point I got dropped from the front group and I was no longer in contention for a medal, I would pull out of the race and recover for the Team Pursuit.\\\"\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4418, \"end\": 4430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.828675473823764e-35, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an agreement\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4173}, {\"ngram\": \"my track coaches\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4195}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4230}, {\"ngram\": \"any point\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4286}, {\"ngram\": \"the front group\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4321}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4355}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 4360, \"to\": 4367}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Luckily for Faulkner and USA Cycling, she had both sparkling form and racing intelligence way beyond her years in the sport.\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4446, \"end\": 4454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3254571354490144e-18, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"USA Cycling\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4470}, {\"ngram\": \"her years\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4544}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only did she deftly avoid the crash from teammate Dygert with 48km to go, she slotted easily into the lead group while race favourites like Kopecky and Lorena Wiebes (Netherlands) had to burn matches chasing.\", \"from\": 4559, \"to\": 4771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4715, \"end\": 4728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorena_Wiebes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorena Wiebes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorena_Wiebes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorena_Wiebes\"}, {\"begin\": 4730, \"end\": 4741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999796718841, \"rank\": 2.031030374290704e-08, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crash\", \"from\": 4589, \"to\": 4598}, {\"ngram\": \"teammate Dygert\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4619}, {\"ngram\": \"48km\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4629}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead group\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4675}, {\"ngram\": \"while race favourites\", \"from\": 4676, \"to\": 4697}, {\"ngram\": \"Kopecky\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4710}, {\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 4755, \"to\": 4762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Vos got away with Hungary's Blanka Vas with just over 20km to go, Faulkner was still in medal contention in the chasing group but appeared to wait to commit fully until the closing kilometres, and stayed focussed on Kopecky.\", \"from\": 4773, \"to\": 5002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4796, \"end\": 4803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9989092100045718, \"rank\": 0.0010919760752016337, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 4806, \"end\": 4816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blanka_Vas\", \"score\": 0.9999999946312528, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Blanka Vas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blanka_Vas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blanka_Vas\"}, {\"begin\": 4844, \"end\": 4852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3254571354490144e-18, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vos\", \"from\": 4778, \"to\": 4781}, {\"ngram\": \"just over 20km\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4836}, {\"ngram\": \"medal contention\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 4882}, {\"ngram\": \"the chasing group\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 4903}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing kilometres\", \"from\": 4947, \"to\": 4969}, {\"ngram\": \"Kopecky\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt quite strong throughout the day, and after the first time up the cobbled climb, I said, I am feeling the best I felt a really long time.\", \"from\": 5004, \"to\": 5148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 5036, \"to\": 5043}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5069}, {\"ngram\": \"the cobbled climb\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am going to go for it and just continue with the race and to earn a medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 5149, \"to\": 5229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 5199, \"to\": 5207}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 5220, \"to\": 5227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, in the scintillating chase with Kopecky, Faulkner made sure her Belgian companion continued to work to close the gap to Vos and Vas, which they did with 4km to go.\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5278, \"end\": 5286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3254571354490144e-18, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}, {\"begin\": 5301, \"end\": 5308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.98230591247806, \"rank\": 0.01801280739823917, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scintillating chase\", \"from\": 5240, \"to\": 5263}, {\"ngram\": \"Kopecky\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5276}, {\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 5346, \"to\": 5353}, {\"ngram\": \"Vos\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5360}, {\"ngram\": \"Vas\", \"from\": 5365, \"to\": 5368}, {\"ngram\": \"4km\", \"from\": 5390, \"to\": 5393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She attacked almost immediately, knowing she would not medal in a sprint against those three riders.\", \"from\": 5401, \"to\": 5501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sprint\", \"from\": 5465, \"to\": 5473}, {\"ngram\": \"those three riders\", \"from\": 5482, \"to\": 5500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, Faulkner will join Dygert, Lily Williams, Olivia Cummins and Tokyo Omnium gold medalist Jen Valente at the Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines velodrome and turn her focus on getting medals for the lot of them.\", \"from\": 5503, \"to\": 5708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5508, \"end\": 5516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3254571354490144e-18, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}, {\"begin\": 5535, \"end\": 5548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lily_Williams\", \"score\": 0.9999241856590325, \"rank\": 7.58198123390823e-05, \"text\": \"Lily Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lily_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lily_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 5550, \"end\": 5556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Dunham\", \"score\": 0.9999999059887204, \"rank\": 9.400676706164518e-08, \"text\": \"Olivia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Dunham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Dunham\"}, {\"begin\": 5557, \"end\": 5564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cummins\", \"score\": 0.9999839816364895, \"rank\": 1.6015921993741403e-05, \"text\": \"Cummins\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cummins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cummins\"}, {\"begin\": 5569, \"end\": 5574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999410575351275, \"rank\": 0.0005897239293916879, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dygert\", \"from\": 5527, \"to\": 5533}, {\"ngram\": \"the Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines velodrome\", \"from\": 5611, \"to\": 5650}, {\"ngram\": \"her focus\", \"from\": 5660, \"to\": 5669}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 5681, \"to\": 5687}, {\"ngram\": \"the lot\", \"from\": 5692, \"to\": 5699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still feel we can earn another medal in Team Pursuit, because we have a really strong team.\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5753, \"end\": 5765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.828675473823764e-35, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another medal\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5749}, {\"ngram\": \"a really strong team\", \"from\": 5783, \"to\": 5803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, yeah, I want to walk away with two medals.\\\"\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 5853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two medals\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 5851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get unlimited access to all of our coverage of the 2024 Olympic Games - including breaking news and analysis reported by our journalists on the ground from every event across road, mountain bike, track and BMX racing as it happens and more.Find out more.\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 6109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6061, \"end\": 6071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999989159401236, \"rank\": 1.08407164745666e-05, \"text\": \"BMX racing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"unlimited access\", \"from\": 5859, \"to\": 5875}, {\"ngram\": \"our coverage\", \"from\": 5886, \"to\": 5898}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5902, \"to\": 5924}, {\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 5946, \"to\": 5950}, {\"ngram\": \"analysis\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 5963}, {\"ngram\": \"our journalists\", \"from\": 5976, \"to\": 5991}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 5995, \"to\": 6005}, {\"ngram\": \"every event\", \"from\": 6011, \"to\": 6022}, {\"ngram\": \"road\", \"from\": 6030, \"to\": 6034}, {\"ngram\": \"mountain bike\", \"from\": 6036, \"to\": 6049}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 6051, \"to\": 6056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Weislo is aCyclingnewsveteran of 20 years.\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6111, \"end\": 6116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"score\": 0.9998199934652982, \"rank\": 0.00018003894222912452, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"aCyclingnewsveteran\", \"from\": 6127, \"to\": 6146}, {\"ngram\": \"20 years\", \"from\": 6150, \"to\": 6158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having joined in 2006, Laura extensively covered the Operacion Puerto doping scandal, the years-long conflict between the UCI and the Tour de France organisers ASO over the creation of the WorldTour, and the downfall of Lance Armstrong and his lifetime ban for doping.\", \"from\": 6160, \"to\": 6428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6183, \"end\": 6188, \"title\": \"